## ğŸ“Š Core Insights
- Clustered users into **3 engagement segments:** Casual Viewers, Binge Watchers, Genre Loyalists
- Users receiving personalized recommendations showed **+18% higher watch-time**
- Heavy watchers retained **40% longer** than casual users
- Genre-loyal users respond best to targeted recommendations

